OL,6,F` Double council tax rates on the top
OL,7,Ftwo property bands to raise #4.4
OL,8,Fbillion. Any extra cash from changes
OL,9,Fto council tax would flow to local
OL,10,Fauthorities rather than central
OL,11,Fgovernment, but Ms Reeves could in
